---
import DefaultLayout from '@layouts/DefaultLayout.astro'
import PageHeader from '@components/PageHeader.astro'
import { Heading, Notification } from 'accessible-astro-components'
import { getCollection } from 'astro:content'
import { Image } from 'astro:assets'
import CallToAction from '@components/CallToAction.astro'
import building1 from '@assets/images/about/building-1.jpg'
import building2 from '@assets/images/about/building-2.jpg'
import dignity from '@assets/images/about/dignity.jpg'
import humility from '@assets/images/about/humility-2.jpg'
import innovation from '@assets/images/about/innovation.jpg'
import justice from '@assets/images/about/justice.jpg'
import powerSharing from '@assets/images/about/power-sharing.jpg'

// Get all portfolio projects
const projects = await getCollection('projects')

// Define approaches with their descriptions
const approaches = [
  {
    title: 'Build relationships',
    description:
      'Relationships are the cornerstone of our work (and lives), and we value them above all else. We build trust and authentic connections with people at every level of our work, especially across lines of power and difference. ',
  },
  {
    title: 'Collaborate',
    description:
      'We relish opportunities to collaborate with and learn from one another--both our team and those with whom we work. We aim to keep everyone in the loop and reach out when we’re not sure about something, knowing that in doing so we are building our collective knowledge and impact.',
  },
  {
    title: 'Be accountable',
    description:
      'Put simply, we do what we say we’re going to do. And when we occasionally fall short, we own that, take corrective action, and do better next time. For us, accountability runs up, down, and sideways.',
  },
  {
    title: 'Focus on the person',
    description:
      'At the center of all systems are people, and we strive to never lose sight of that. Whether it’s going off the agenda when a colleague seems like they’re not okay, or making sure someone’s basic needs are met even when it’s a little outside of our scope, we adapt to the needs of the person at the center of it all and offer each other empathy and grace.',
  },
  {
    title: 'Engage in direct service',
    description:
      'Every Jaydot team member spends valuable time on the ground. We work hard to witness and understand the realities that our clients—and staff—face every day so we can most effectively address them. ',
  },
]
---

<DefaultLayout
  title="About"
  description="I have reset the sensors to scan for frequencies outside the usual range. By emitting harmonic vibrations to shatter the lattices."
>
  <PageHeader
    title="About Us"
    subtitle="I have reset the sensors to scan for frequencies outside the usual range. By emitting harmonic vibrations to shatter the lattices. We will monitor and adjust the frequency of the resonators. He has this ability of instantly interpreting and extrapolating any verbal communication he hears."
    bgType="gradient"
  />

  <section class="my-16">
    <div class="container space-y-12">
      <div>
        <Heading level="h2" class="mb-6">Our history</Heading>
        <div class="mb-20">
          <Image
            class="md:float-left w-100 md:mr-6 mb-6"
            src={building1}
            alt="FIXME"
            decoding="async"
            loading="lazy"
          />
          <div>
            <p class="mb-4">
              With the first link, the chain is forged. The first speech censored, the first thought forbidden, the
              first freedom denied, chains us all irrevocably. Your will to survive, your love of life, your passion to
              know ... Everything that is truest and best in all species of beings has been revealed to you.
            </p>
            <p class="mb-4">
              Those are the qualities that make a civilization worthy to survive. Look at these three words written
              larger than all the rest, and with special pride never written before or since -- tall words, proudly
              saying "We the people" ... these words and the words that follow ... must apply to everyone or they mean
              nothing. I object to intellect without discipline; I object to power without constructive purpose. Make It
              So!
            </p>
            <p class="mb-4">
              When dreams become more important than reality, you give up travel, building, creating; you even forget
              how to repair the machines left behind by your ancestors. You just sit living and reliving other lives
              left behind in the thought records. Leave bigotry in your quarters; there's no room for it on the bridge.
              You know the greatest danger facing us is ourselves, and irrational fear of the unknown. There is no such
              thing as the unknown. Only things temporarily hidden, temporarily not understood.
            </p>
            <p>
              Now, I don't pretend to tell you how to find happiness and love, when every day is a struggle to survive.
              But I do insist that you do survive, because the days and the years ahead are worth living for! For
              everything, there is a first time. Do you know the old Klingon proverb that revenge is a dish best served
              cold? It is very cold — in space.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <Heading level="h2" class="mb-2">Our values</Heading>
        <p class="italic">We strive to embody these six core values in our daily work.</p>
        <div class="masonry sm:masonry-sm md:masonry-md gap-8 mt-10">
          <div class="mb-4 border-2 rounded-lg border-(--brand-orange) p-4 md:w-120 break-inside-avoid">
            <Image
              class="w-300 cover rounded-t-lg relative"
              src={dignity}
              alt="FIXME"
              decoding="async"
              loading="lazy"
            />
            <div class="rounded-b-lg bg-(--brand-primary) p-4 text-(--brand-light-olive)">
              <Heading level="h3" class="mb-2">Dignity</Heading>
              <p>We value the inherent dignity, humanity, self-determination, and worth of all people.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="mb-4 border-2 rounded-lg border-(--brand-orange) p-4 md:w-120 break-inside-avoid">
            <Image
              class="w-full cover rounded-t-lg relative"
              src={justice}
              alt="FIXME"
              decoding="async"
              loading="lazy"
            />
            <div class="rounded-b-lg bottom-0 left-0 bg-(--brand-primary)/90 p-4 text-(--brand-light-olive)">
              <Heading level="h3" class="mb-2">Justice</Heading>
              <p>
                Many of the challenges we seek to address are a direct result of intersecting systems of oppression, in
                particular anti-Black racism. We are committed to honoring people’s unique histories, perspectives, and
                ways of being, and working towards a system in which all people are free.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="mb-4 border-2 rounded-lg border-(--brand-orange) p-4 md:w-120 break-inside-avoid">
            <Image
              class="w-full cover rounded-t-lg relative"
              src={innovation}
              alt="FIXME"
              decoding="async"
              loading="lazy"
            />
            <div class="rounded-b-lg bottom-0 left-0 bg-(--brand-primary)/90 p-4 text-(--brand-light-olive)">
              <Heading level="h3" class="mb-2">Innovation</Heading>
              <p>
                We work to identify the gaps and possibilities in the systems within which we operate and work with our
                partners to craft innovative solutions. We are not bound by what is—we adapt to changing circumstances and
                focus on what can be.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="mb-4 border-2 rounded-lg border-(--brand-orange) p-4 md:w-120 break-inside-avoid">
            <Image
              class="w-full cover rounded-t-lg relative"
              src={humility}
              alt="FIXME"
              decoding="async"
              loading="lazy"
            />
            <div class="rounded-b-lg bottom-0 left-0 bg-(--brand-primary)/90 p-4 text-(--brand-light-olive)">
              <Heading level="h3" class="mb-2">Humility</Heading>
              <p>
                We are always learning and thus making mistakes. We are committed to reflecting on, owning, and learning
                from our collective experiences.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="mb-4 border-2 rounded-lg border-(--brand-orange) p-4 md:w-120 break-inside-avoid">
            <Image
              class="w-full cover rounded-t-lg relative"
              src={powerSharing}
              alt="FIXME"
              decoding="async"
              loading="lazy"
            />
            <div class="rounded-b-lg bottom-0 left-0 bg-(--brand-primary)/90 p-4 text-(--brand-light-olive)">
              <Heading level="h3" class="mb-2">Power sharing</Heading>
              <p>
                We strive to build the capacity of our team and the communities we work with by transferring our
                collective knowledge, credibility, and power.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="mb-4 border-2 rounded-lg border-(--brand-orange) p-4 md:w-120 break-inside-avoid">
            <Image
              class="w-full cover rounded-t-lg relative"
              src={building2}
              alt="FIXME"
              decoding="async"
              loading="lazy"
            />
            <div class="rounded-b-lg bottom-0 left-0 bg-(--brand-primary)/90 p-4 text-(--brand-light-olive)">
              <Heading level="h3" class="mb-2">Holistic thinking</Heading>
              <p>
                We are involved in all aspects of our field, from macro policy to the ground level, and believe that they
                are deeply connected. We are dedicated to establishing connections to ensure that systems are responsive
                to the needs of the communities with which we work.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      <div class="mt-20">
        <Heading level="h2" class="mb-2">Our approach</Heading>
        <p class="mb-12 italic">
          Just as important as what we do is how we do it. Here's our approach to achieving our mission.
        </p>
        <div class="">
          {
            approaches.map((page) => (
              <article>
                <Heading level="h3" size="h6" class="mb-3">
                  {page.title}
                </Heading>
                <p class="mb-3">{page.description}</p>
              </article>
            ))
          }
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <CallToAction />

    <div class="mt-20 italic text-sm">Thanks to Robert Benson and Gus Powell for photos on this page.</div>

  </section>
</DefaultLayout>

<style>
  article {
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color-subtle);
    border-radius: var(--radius-large);
    background-color: var(--background-color);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    padding: 1rem;
  }
</style>